      <p>
        <s><name type="person">Bianca L.</name><add>(18 years)</add> from <name type="geo">Germany</name> went to <choice><orig>a</orig><reg>an</reg></choice> <name type="misc">Education Centre</name> for children located in a slum of <name type="geo">Delhi</name> in <name type="geo">India</name>.</s>
        <s>She helped teach the kids <choice><orig>english</orig><reg>English</reg></choice> grammar.</s>
      </p>
      <p>
        <s>She described the kids to be the most lovable littel ones who <choice><orig>capured</orig><reg>captured</reg></choice> her heart the second she entered the room.</s>
      </p>
      <p>
        <s><name type="person">Bianca</name> now <choice><orig>sais</orig><reg>says</reg></choice> that even though these kids don't have it as well as the ones in other <choice><orig>countrys</orig><reg>countries</reg></choice> they were still little bundles of joy.</s>
        <s>Spending time with them laughing, reading, clapping were the most valuable of her days.</s>
      </p>
